d can be\napplied to solve a broad class of problems, particularly approximating\ndistribution functions, computing financial Greeks, and estimating risk\nquantities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Nov 2021 20:23:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2022 16:16:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-24"}
