y is demonstrated on three\ncase studies: a model for longitudinal flight control by Branicky, an automatic\ncruise controller, and Brockett's nonholonomic integrator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Nov 2021 22:40:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 19:09:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-12"}
