od. The semi-analytical solver, combined with\nMonte Carlo simulations, is then applied to assess the sensitivity and\nuncertainty of various fluid and subsurface parameters. The proposed can serve\nas a quick diagnostic tool to evaluate lost-circulation in drilling operations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Nov 2021 07:35:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-04"}
