 and (vii) the maximum-height independent towers\nproblem, in which we want to erect vertical towers of maximum height over a\n1.5-dimensional terrain so that no pair of tower tips are mutually visible.\n  We obtain significantly improved solutions for problems (i), (ii) and (vi),\nand new efficient solutions to the other problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Nov 2021 07:48:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 28 Nov 2021 09:35:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 14 Jul 2022 11:25:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-15"}
