 all-in-one\npicture of non-covalent interactions which provide the more stable\nconfigurations, also including interactions other than H-bonds. Such\ndescriptors are more informative than previously used quantities and can be\nused as universal input to better inform new machine learning studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Nov 2021 09:13:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-04"}
