ons in $E$ are in agreement with spectral\nresolutions in the corresponding order unit space.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Nov 2021 12:10:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2022 11:34:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 26 Oct 2022 09:26:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
